so fucking grim all the time.

545
00:58:15.619 --> 00:58:17.871
Come on. boys.
let's go kill some boar!

546
00:58:28.090 --> 00:58:29.591
Come on. you.

547
00:59:45.959 --> 00:59:48.754
- Stop! Stop.
-

548
